{"tid":473783,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"前新聞主播齊集到賀 林燕玲嫁金融才俊　向黃婉曼取生仔經","createTime":"2017-11-19T13:53:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-19T14:09:30.000Z","uid":84436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ea71be075e66089d45bddcca236b90967fc15055","tid":473783,"uid":84436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T13:53:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20171119/20218799\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171119%2F20218799&d=EqQJC1E0smmW6Oa1XPZok54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=e962b207\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171119%2F20218799&h=f019565e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20171119/20218799</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無綫前主播小飛俠林燕玲戀情一向低調神秘，她去年與年輕一歲的金融才俊葉浩文出席公開場合讓感情曝光。二人感情發展迅速，本月初在海外秘密註冊結為夫婦，昨日二人在fb才公告婚事，並搞小型結婚派對宴請圈中友人，她笑言要向好友黃婉曼取生仔經生B。<br />\n<br />\n現年39歲、人稱「小飛俠」的林燕玲（Ruby）效力過無綫做新聞主播，現職為林建岳的麗新集團傳訊部副總裁。Ruby戀事一向低調，去年與於復星資本任職執行總經理的葉浩文（Kirk）出席活動，戀情才曝光，據知兩人皆熱愛跑步，不時與一班財經界朋友一齊練跑才跑出愛火花"},{"pid":"971c0acc462d1905dcc735ae9c99f05885bd8e77","tid":473783,"uid":27458,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T14:01:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>恭喜爆房玲<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"8bef3f0e26a26a8af832158aadf70e40886c317c","tid":473783,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T14:02:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"730bcba021fc5d07dbd55b558c93f128a6f9d038","tid":473783,"uid":54516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T14:09:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>39歲收經未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n林心如40歲先大肚,不過35以上先有咗會大風險D."}]}